{"tid":2151364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"以傘襲擊追捕學生便衣警 女文員獲撤控改守行為","createTime":"2020-08-11T10:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T12:20:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"292d780d693548b80f35a007a712eb1cfa05763d","tid":2151364,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:52:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/PEHEMJ5QBPKTNMMWQ5FE6JNOPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FPEHEMJ5QBPKTNMMWQ5FE6JNOPA%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=7407550d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FPEHEMJ5QBPKTNMMWQ5FE6JNOPA%2F&h=ad158571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/PEHEMJ5QBPKTNMMWQ5FE6JNOPA/</a><br />\n<br />\n網民於去年11月3日發起「七區行街」，其中沙田新城市廣場有市民聚集，繼而爆發警民衝突，多人被捕。其中三名未成年男生在附近的百步梯「換裝」時遭截查，被搜出鎚、雷射筆等物品，其間女文員用傘襲擊追捕三人的便衣警。四人分別被控管有攻擊性武器、襲警等罪，案件今在沙田裁判法院提堂，其中一名男生認罪，案件押後索取感化報告再判刑，女文員則在同意案情下獲准以簽保守行為方式處理，控罪獲撤銷。"},{"pid":"e7bb7a161f3f986fcf26922e72756af70774ad8a","tid":2151364,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b93b06f9850ca6a715ef1712841e5fa999255af7","tid":2151364,"uid":276440,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"女文員一世平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4fd4de80db2e41ddf171108aee6ced94cfd130","tid":2151364,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7bb7a161f3f986fcf26922e72756af70774ad8a","tid":2151364,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/